  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "My Garden is the debut studio album by American recording artist Kat Dahlia. It was released on January 13, 2015, by Epic Records, distributed by Vested in Culture. The album was supported by two singles; \"Gangsta\" and \"Crazy\", as well as the iTunes' \"instant gratification\" tracks; \"Mirror\" and \"Clocks\".\nIn January 2014, Complex listed My Garden, as the forty-sixth most anticipated album of 2014. After several delays, from being scheduled to be released in February 2014, to being rescheduled to September 2014, in October 2014, Epic Records settled in January 2015.",
